figgy.title: Enable CDL workflow for EAD objects

comments.body:
The latest I have heard is that this is really "Limit access to certain Figgy items to a class". We could do that in a variety of ways:
* Access token links added to Canvas/BB course
* Add new role for class access and add the students enrolled in the course to that role in Figgy
* Add a notion of classes to Figgy, and check a list of course enrollment to allow/deny access (@kevinreiss Can we get a reliable list of students enrolled in a particular course?)
